<a name="2564"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Last Chance to Get Your Best Customers to CES for FREE </div>
<br />
<IMG height=168 hspace=10 src="/print/images/content/EX_invite.jpg" width=130 align=right vspace=10>You'll be at CES this January, but the question is: Will your buyers and other key customers be there, too? <BR><BR>Make sure they are – and help them duck the registration fee – by sending them official <A href="/print/exhibitors/sponsorships/freeOpps.asp" target=_blank>2009 CES Exhibitor Invitations</A>. This <A href="/print/exhibitors/sponsorships/freeOpps.asp" target=_blank>invitation</A>, which contains a special priority code, provides your guest with FREE advance registration to the International CES up until December 15, 2008. Budget savings have never been more important. Free registration could be the deciding factor for your customers to register and attend CES. <A href="/print/exhibitors/sponsorships/freeOpps.asp" target=_blank>Download this invitation</A> now or order printed invites (free of charge) today.

