<a name="2562"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Exhibitor Staff Guides Now Available!</div>
<br />
Are you putting together a 2009 International CES on-site staff guide for your company?&nbsp; If so, we just made it a lot easier for you to create a guide for your colleagues to use on-site. Please visit our <A href="/print/exhibitors/resources/A92402F9C8E7404CB0D8151FA0E3B99E.htm" target=_blank>web-site</A> to choose from an array of helpful documents – from badge holder pickup information to a list of suggested restaurants – or simply print out a <A href="/print/exhibitors/resources/A92402F9C8E7404CB0D8151FA0E3B99E.htm" target=_blank>complete staff guide</A> that we have put together for you at the top of the page. You may want to include a personalized cover, your booth number and company contact information.&nbsp; Otherwise, we have taken care of the rest for you.

